# Phase 4: Langflow & Orchestration — The Abyss Nervous System

## IDENTITY
- Document: SENTRA-ABYSS-004
- Owner: Dr. Ferdi Iskandar — Founder & Chief Architect, Sentra Healthcare AI
- Classification: PROPRIETARY & CONFIDENTIAL
- Phase Duration: 5–6 weeks
- Langflow Version: ≥ 1.6.4 (MANDATORY — CVE-2025-3248 patched)

## PRIME DIRECTIVE
All AI flow executions MUST route through `apps/orchestrator` — the Orchestrator Gateway API.
NO application may call Langflow APIs directly.
NO flow may be deployed to production without passing Promptfoo (>95%) + Ragas (>0.85) quality gates.

